## New Components

### 1. `apps/dashboard/src/components/projects/project-card.tsx`

A card component that displays a single project's information. Clicking the card navigates to the project detail page.

**Props:**
```typescript
interface ProjectCardProps {
  project: {
    id: string;
    name: string;
    slug: string;
    githubRepoFullName: string | null;
    framework: string | null;
    latestDeployment: {
      id: string;
      status: string;
      url: string | null;
      createdAt: string;
    } | null;
  };
}
```

**Layout:**
```
+--------------------------------------------------+
| My App                           [ready] badge   |
|                                                   |
| georgele/my-app (GitHub link icon)                |
|                                                   |
| https://my-app.yourdomain.dev                    |
| Deployed 2 hours ago                              |
