- Timestamp: `text-xs text-gray-400`, displayed as relative time ("2 hours ago")
- Entire card is wrapped in a `<Link>` to `/projects/{id}`
- Framework indicator: small pill showing `nextjs`, `dockerfile`, or `static`

### 2. `apps/dashboard/src/components/projects/status-badge.tsx`

A reusable status badge component used across the dashboard.

**Props:**
```typescript
interface StatusBadgeProps {
  status: "queued" | "building" | "deploying" | "ready" | "failed" | "archived";
  size?: "sm" | "md";
}
```

**Color mapping:**
| Status | Background | Text | Dot Color |
|--------|-----------|------|-----------|
| `queued` | `bg-gray-100` | `text-gray-700` | `bg-gray-400` |
| `building` | `bg-yellow-100` | `text-yellow-700` | `bg-yellow-400` (animate-pulse) |
| `deploying` | `bg-blue-100` | `text-blue-700` | `bg-blue-400` (animate-pulse) |
| `ready` | `bg-green-100` | `text-green-700` | `bg-green-400` |
| `failed` | `bg-red-100` | `text-red-700` | `bg-red-400` |
| `archived` | `bg-gray-100` | `text-gray-500` | `bg-gray-300` |

**Structure:**
```
[ * Ready ]
```
A small colored dot before the capitalized status text. Pulsing animation for in-progress statuses (building, deploying).

